	*** runtime/{Clib/crgc.c,Jlib/foreign.java,CSlib/foreign.cs}: fix
	reading overflowing integers.
	

Thu May  7 05:08:23 CEST 2009 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** configure: accommodate BSD sendfile (in addition to Linux sendfile).
	

Mon May  4 15:40:46 CEST 2009 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** comptime/Object/nil.scm: fix bignum that used to be an invalid
	type for class fields.
	

