	be defined within interpreter code).
	

Wed Jan 23 10:54:20 CET 2008 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** runtime/Clib/cports.c: add EINTR test to sysread_with_timeout.
	

Mon Jan 21 11:06:41 CET 2008 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** runtime: Complete re-implementation of the dynamic environment
	support. In particular, the environment is now explicitly used 
	by low-level macro and the environment is passed to EVMEANING.
	This improves the performance of EVAL in multi-threaded applications
	by about 25%.
	

Fri Jan 18 08:07:21 CET 2008 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** api/pthread: Improve pthread implementation in order to let
	threads non initialized by Bigloo (for instance, those created by
	gstreamer) to be still usable by the Bigloo runtime.
	

