	* examples/DNet: add an example illustrating how to connect
	Scheme code and C# code.
	

Tue Jan  8 20:37:14 CET 2008 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** runtime/Unsafe/{md5,base64}.scm: fix an initialization problem.
	MD5 must initialize BASE64 but the former "use" clause of MD5 was
	not forcing this initialization. The "use" has been replaced by an
	"import".

	
