Sun Dec 30 09:29:41 CET 2007 (Manuel Serrano):

	* Cigloo: add identifier pretty-print rules.
	

Wed Dec 26 16:39:32 CET 2007 (Manuel Serrano):

	* comptime/{Coerce/*,Init/parseargs/Engine/param}.scm: add the
	-safee and -unafee that enable the compiler to compile in unsafe
	type mode the standard calls but the functional calls. This can be
	used to compile in unsafe a library while exporting a library
	whose calls from the evaluator (eval) are still type checked.

	*** runtime/{Llib/type.scm,Include/bigloo.h}: fix a typing error
	in $obj->void*.
	

