Sat Aug  4 16:00:56 CEST 2007 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** comptime/Ast/venv.scm: fix a bug in the restoration of inlined
	library function. The type replacement was not correctly propagated
	inside the sifun-orignal-body field. Hence, the compiler raised errors
        such as "pair expected, pair provided" because the ast coming from
	inlining library function was containing several different instances
	of the same types.
	

