	* comptime/Cfa/specialize.scm: alias int and long specializing
	arithmetic operators.


Wed Nov  8 12:07:54 CET 2006 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** runtime/Llib/date.scm: second arithmetic has been removed
	(as it was an alias of elong arithmetic).
	

