	add FILE-NAME-CANONICALIZE!.
	

Sat Oct 22 15:05:04 CEST 2005 (Manuel Serrano):

	*** runtime/Clib/csocket.c: fix a bug in non blocking socket.
	The result of a connection is now tested with getsockopt.
	

